        UC37[Link/Unlink Authorizations]
        UC38[Create Multisig Proposals]
        UC39[Approve/Reject Multisig Proposals]
        UC40[Backup Antelope Account]
        UC41[Create EOS Account via EVM]
        UC42[Import EOS Account via EVM]
    end

    %% Use Cases - Settings & Configuration
    subgraph "Settings & Configuration"
        UC43[Change App Theme]
        UC44[Select Language]
        UC45[Set Default Currency]
        UC46[Manage Custom Networks]
        UC47[Configure Notifications]
        UC48[Manage Security Settings]
        UC49[Manage Contacts]
